RESULT: The control module internal supply appears to be at approximately 12 V (Control Input Cable (+): ~11.99 V; Control Input Cable (−): ~0 V), indicating the electronics are powered from the +12 V input side. The relay’s switched node is at ~0.36 V (Control Relay / Control Output Cable (+)), and the relay contacts did not open or cause a supply dip during the observed lamp dropout.
